description: Charming penthouse condo in a prime Westside location, amidst the ever evolving new Washington Village neighborhood! Totally renovated in 2017, this move-in-ready gem features a bright and airy kitchen/living area bathed in natural light, with direct access to TWO private outdoor spaces, including an incredible ~265 sq ft private roof deck offering sweeping city views. The condo features two queen-sized bedrooms, a tile bath, in-unit laundry, and an additional back deck with storage. Located on Loring Street--a one-way street just steps from West Broadway, Washington Village, and South Boston's best shopping, dining, and health/wellness spots. Easy highway and MBTA access. Embrace the Southie lifestyle with this perfect home!
